## Best Practices

1. Component Structure

- Keep components focused
- Use composition over inheritance
- Extract reusable logic to hooks
- Implement proper TypeScript types
- Follow [Core Concepts](mdc:.cursor/rules/core.mdc) file organization

2. State Management

- Use TanStack Query for server state
- Use minimal local state
- Avoid useEffect when possible
- Keep state close to usage

3. Performance

- React compiler handles optimization
- No need for memo/callback/useMemo
- Use proper keys for lists
- Implement proper loading states

4. Accessibility

- Use semantic HTML
- Implement ARIA attributes
- Support keyboard navigation
- Test with screen readers

5. Forms

- Use controlled components sparingly
- Implement proper validation
- Handle all form states
- Show clear error messages

6. Styling

- Use Tailwind utility classes
- Avoid inline styles
- Follow design system
- Maintain responsive design
